  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whenever you are trading for equipment, you can attempt a Diplomacy or Deception skill check against the trader's Will DC. If you succeed, treat one item you are offering up for barter as if it was worth 1 barter more. If you critically succeed, treat it as if it was worth 2 barter more. If you critically fail, the trader refuses to do business with you. You can only do this once per day with an individual trader.</p>",
